<td style="padding-bottom:0.6em;"><a href="/wiki/Hurrian_language" title="Hurrian language">Hurrian</a>&#160;<span style="font-weight:bold;">·</span>  <a href="/wiki/Hittite_language" title="Hittite language">Hittite</a></td>
